# @param {String} s
# @param {Integer} k
# @return {Integer}
def beautiful_substrings(s, k)
    count = 0
    n = s.length
    vowels = 'aeiou'

    # Precompute vowel and consonant counts
    vowel_count = Array.new(n+1, 0)
    consonant_count = Array.new(n+1, 0)

    (1..n).each do |i|
        vowel_count[i] = vowel_count[i-1]
        consonant_count[i] = consonant_count[i-1]
        if vowels.include?(s[i-1])
            vowel_count[i] += 1
        else
            consonant_count[i] += 1
        end
    end

    # Iterate over all substrings
    (0...n).each do |i|
        (i+1..n).each do |j|
            v = vowel_count[j] - vowel_count[i]
            c = consonant_count[j] - consonant_count[i]
            if v == c && (v * c) % k == 0
                count += 1
            end
        end
    end

    count
end
